<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Glosa&amp;action=edit&amp;section=19" title="Edit section: Numbers">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Numbers">Numbers</span></h3>
<p>The following table uses a <a href="/wiki/Full-stop" title="Full-stop" class="mw-redirect">period</a> (.) to represent groups of three zeros (0).</p>
<table class="wikitable" style="text-align:center">
<caption>Numerals</caption>
