<li id="cite_note-4"><b><a href="#cite_ref-4">^</a></b> Bartlett, Paul O. «Critiques of individual planned languages» <a href="http://www.panix.com/~bartlett/ial.html" class="external autonumber" rel="nofollow">[5]</a>. Updated: 2005-11-30.</li>
<li id="cite_note-5"><b><a href="#cite_ref-5">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.englishtexts.org/praying.pdf" class="external text" rel="nofollow">Praying Together</a></li>
</ol>
